Class AbstractSubscriptionDescriptionItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.poesys.db.dto.AbstractDto
      • org.phoenixbioinformatics.api.db.api.AbstractSubscriptionDescriptionItem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.poesys.db.dto.IDbDto, com.poesys.db.dto.IObserver, com.poesys.db.dto.ISubject, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<com.poesys.db.dto.IDbDto>, ISubscriptionDescriptionItem
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SubscriptionDescriptionItem

    public abstract class AbstractSubscriptionDescriptionItem
extends com.poesys.db.dto.AbstractDto
implements ISubscriptionDescriptionItem

    A data-access layer data-transfer object for the SubscriptionDescriptionItem. This class is an abstract class that contains AndroMDA generated code; change nothing in this class. Instead, override any methods in the concrete subclass generated in the same package. AndroMDA will overwrite this class each time you run it but will never overwrite the concrete subclass.

    A specific item of descriptive text

    Stereotypes:

    • CompositeKey
    • Persistent

    Class is read/write: true

    Author:
    Poesys/DB Cartridge
